## Built-in AI Models — Free Embeddings

Edge Functions have a built-in AI model runner — no API key needed, no cost per call.
Available model: `gte-small` (384 dimensions, English text, fast, free).

Compare to OpenAI text-embedding-3-small: lower quality but zero cost, zero latency penalty.
Use case: search within your own content where perfect semantic accuracy is less critical.

### Generate embeddings with built-in model
```typescript
// No imports needed — Session is a global in the Edge Runtime
Deno.serve(async (req: Request) => {
  const { text } = await req.json()

  // Built-in model — runs locally in Edge Runtime, no external API call
  const session = new Supabase.ai.Session('gte-small')
  const embedding = await session.run(text, {
    mean_pool: true,
    normalize: true,
  })

  // embedding is a Float32Array of 384 dimensions
  return new Response(JSON.stringify({ embedding: Array.from(embedding) }))
})
```

### pgvector schema for built-in model (384 dimensions — NOT 1536)
```sql
-- If using built-in model, use 384 dimensions (not 1536)
ALTER TABLE documents ADD COLUMN embedding_small VECTOR(384);

CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION match_documents_small(
  query_embedding VECTOR(384),
  match_threshold FLOAT DEFAULT 0.78,
  match_count INT DEFAULT 5
)
RETURNS TABLE(id BIGINT, content TEXT, similarity FLOAT)
LANGUAGE sql STABLE AS $$
  SELECT id, content, 1 - (embedding_small <=> query_embedding) AS similarity
  FROM documents
  WHERE 1 - (embedding_small <=> query_embedding) > match_threshold
  ORDER BY embedding_small <=> query_embedding
  LIMIT match_count;
$$;
```

### When to use built-in vs OpenAI
```
Built-in (gte-small, 384 dims):
  ✅ Free — zero cost per embedding
  ✅ No API key needed
  ✅ Faster (no external API call)
  ✅ Good enough for: search within your own content, doc similarity, FAQ matching
  ❌ English only
  ❌ Lower quality than OpenAI for complex semantic tasks

OpenAI (text-embedding-3-small, 1536 dims):
  ✅ Higher quality semantic understanding
  ✅ Multilingual
  ✅ Better for: cross-language search, nuanced similarity
  ❌ $0.02 per 1M tokens
  ❌ External API call (~100-300ms)
  ❌ Requires OPENAI_API_KEY secret
```

